getReservoir


public ConditionQuantity getReservoir(WellPosition wellPosition)



    

    
Get the specified ConditionQuantity in this TrialPlate at the
    specified WellPosition. Note that the WellPosition's subposition is ignored
    and the reservoir subposition from the PlateType is used instead.

    

    

    

    

        
Parameters:

        
wellPosition - - the WellPosition at which to add
        to this ConditionQuantity

        
reservoir - - the ConditionQuantity to add to this
        TrialPlate
